videos.description: NC State's Dennis Smith Jr. misses a 3-Point shot and Abdul-Malik Abu gets the put-back dunk.
videos.headline: NC State gets the two-handed put-back slam

videos.description: NC State's Maverick Rowan finds an open Abdul-Malik Abu who throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Abu slams another powerful dunk

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson hits a 3-Pointer, gets a steal off the ensuining inbounds pass and assists on a Ahmed Hill 3-Pointer.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech hits two 3-Pointers in 12 seconds

videos.description: NC State's Abdul-Malik Abu and Dennis Smith Jr. both score with two-handed dunks on consecutive possessions.
videos.headline: NC State gets a pair of dunks on back-to-back possessions

videos.description: NC State's Dennis Smith Jr. uses a stop-and-go move to get by multiple Virginia Tech defenders
videos.headline: Dennis Smith Jr. splits two defenders on his way to another huge dunk

videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson finds Abdul-Malik Abu for another dunk.
videos.headline: Abdul-Malik Abu throws down a monster one-handed dunk

videos.description: NC State's Abdul-Malik Abu has another one-handed slam dunk. NC State's Dennis Smith Jr. gets a steal and a 180 dunk.
videos.headline: Abu throws down another dunk, only to be followed up by a steal and another incredible dunk from Dennis Smith Jr.

videos.description: NC State's Maverick Rowan lobs up an alley-oop for Abdul-Malik Abu to give NC State a 99-77 lead.
videos.headline: Abdul-Malik Abu throws in an alley-oop slam with time winding down

videos.description: NC State's Darius Hicks feeds Shaun Kirk for the alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: NC State caps off win with another alley-oop dunk
